Package org.js4ms.io.net

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MulticastEndpoint
    Interface exposed by objects that forward multicast datagrams as requested using the join and leave methods.
    UdpEndpoint
    A DuplexChannel used to send and receive UdpDatagram objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UdpDatagram
    A representation of a UDP datagram.
    UdpDatagramPayloadSource
    A MessageSource that receives UDP packets via a UdpEndpoint and sends the datagram payload to an OutputChannel.
    UdpDatagramSource
    A MessageSource that receives UDP datagrams via a UdpEndpoint and sends the datagram to an OutputChannel.
    UdpInputChannel
    An InputChannel that can be used to receive UdpDatagram instances from a UdpEndpoint.
    UdpOutputChannel
    An OutputChannel that can be used to send UdpDatagram instances to a UdpEndpoint.
    UdpPacketOutputChannel
    An OutputChannel that can be used to send a byte array containing an RTP/RTCP packet to a specific address and port via UDP.
    UdpSocketEndpoint
    A UdpEndpoint implementation that uses a DatagramChannel to provide transport.
